{"tid":2450392,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《一秒拳王》開畫票房稱冠","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2151730d2e9d86e212c5bd8600d8f515cd659fc2","tid":2450392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/VFKTNI2KYJABTFW477AUZP257A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FVFKTNI2KYJABTFW477AUZP257A%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=b94c7e54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FVFKTNI2KYJABTFW477AUZP257A%2F&h=bf103820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/VFKTNI2KYJABTFW477AUZP257A/</a><br />\n<br />\n《一秒拳王》開畫票房稱冠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KMBmyD2j1IP1snBxeyedKeZunw8=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U3ORDKQSJ5A6DM66I3MI2YPJRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKMBmyD2j1IP1snBxeyedKeZunw8%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU3ORDKQSJ5A6DM66I3MI2YPJRQ.jpg&h=f5b0f8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■趙善恆（左）與張建聲帶童星熊倬樂謝票，他呼籲觀眾入場欣賞《一秒拳王》。<br />\n<br />\n周國賢主演及由樂隊ToNick主音趙善恆主演和執導的電影《一秒拳王》，早前上映優先場反應已相當熱烈。電影前日正式上映，單日票房收37.3萬元成為開畫冠軍，連帶優先場累積票房。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n趙善恆、張建聲及於《一》片演周國賢囝囝的童星熊倬樂，前日親身到戲院謝票，順便呼籲觀眾入場收看，趙善恆在到戲院謝票時說︰「香港嘅電影係唔會死，我哋一定會拍多啲好戲畀大家睇。」他今日及明日會率領周國賢與熊倬樂在全港各區跑足13場謝票。另外，《一》片已入圍6月在意大利舉行的烏甸尼遠東電影節，不過因應疫情，趙善恆未必可以親赴當地出席。"}]}